<h1> formatting
 </h1>
<p>
==bold== and //italic//, the easy-to-type way, and
*bold* and _italic_, the nice-to-read way. All of these
line breaks
are ignored and this is
one paragraph

<blockquote> A quote - it&#39;s just words!
 </blockquote>
</p>
<h2> media
 </h2>
<p>
media are customizable. &#39;image&#39; and &#39;video&#39; are built-in. they must appear on their own line
image

<a href="https://web.site/img.jpg"> A fire
 </a>
shortcut for the above: !

<a href="xyz"> xyz
 </a>
video

<a href="http://web.site/vid.mp4">  </a>
</p>
<h1> lists
 </h1>
<p>
</p>
<ul>
<li> lists are easy to type, no line prefixes needed  </li>
<li> one item goes on each line. Bold/italic etc. are processed  </li>
<li> To add sub-lists, just nest lists  </li>
<li> this is an ordered list:  </li>
<li> <ol>
<li> eat  </li>
<li> sleep  </li>
<li> repeat  </li>
</ol> </li>
</ul>
<p>
</p>
